Did you know that 90% of South East Asians are lactose-intolerant? Each carton of Arla Lactose-free milk has been filtered to remove lactase and break down any remaining sugars to ensure that even the most delicate tummies can enjoy the taste and nutrition of real fresh milk! Storage Instruction: Keep Refrigerated. Do not microwave.
Ingredients Whole milk, lactase.
Allergens contains: milk
Storage: Chill before use to enjoy the best taste. Store in a cool, dry place. Once opened treat like fresh milk and use within 3 days. After each use, reclose and refrigerate at once. ______________________________________________________________________________
